OL,3,CScottish Borders Council leader
OL,4,Claunches rap song
OL,6,FThe leader of Scottish Borders Council
OL,7,Fis releasing a rap track.
OL,9,FIt's called 'Little Man' and includes
OL,10,Freferences to the south of Scotland.
OL,12,FConservative Councillor Euan Jardine -
OL,13,Fwho performs under the name Euan J -
OL,14,Fhas led the council since 2022.
OL,16,FHe says writing lyrics helps him to
OL,17,Fdestress and he hopes to inspire
OL,18,Fothers to be creative and follow their
OL,19,Fpassions.
