OL,3,CScottish Borders Council leader
OL,4,Claunches rap song
OL,6,F"Don't get put in a box, don't fall
OL,7,Finto stereotypes. I'm five foot one, I
OL,8,Fused to play basketball, I used to
OL,9,Frun, why can't I rap?
OL,11,F"I'm sure some will say they didn't
OL,12,Fhave it on their bingo card for 2025,
OL,13,Fthe council leader making a rap track,
OL,14,Fbut this is who I am, I'm not hiding
OL,15,Fwho I am.
OL,17,F"Rap gets a really bad rep for what it
OL,18,Fis. A lot of people think it's
OL,19,Fviolent, no. Rap is one of the purest
OL,20,Fforms of lyricism in the world, if not
OL,21,Fthe purest, for me."
