OL,3,CScottish Borders Council leader
OL,4,Claunches rap song
OL,6,FHe's also planning to release an album
OL,7,Fcalled Shepherd's Son.
OL,9,FHe said: "My dad was a shepherd, I'm
OL,10,Falso a Christian and Jesus is a
OL,11,Fshepherd. So there'll be a whole
OL,12,Fintrospective album, and hopefully,
OL,13,Fwho knows, performing at the MacArts
OL,14,For volunteer hall soon."
OL,16,FLittle Man will be released on Spotify
OL,17,Fon Friday 23 May.
